Bootstrap: docker
From: python:3.13-slim
Stage: build

%files
    config.py /opt/martyn_evaluator/config.py
    data_loader.py /opt/martyn_evaluator/data_loader.py
    evaluator_content_handler.py /opt/martyn_evaluator/evaluator_content_handler.py
    evaluator_metrics_calculator.py /opt/martyn_evaluator/evaluator_metrics_calculator.py
    evaluator_RestAPI.py /opt/martyn_evaluator/evaluator_RestAPI.py

%environment
     # Prevent automatic binding of host directories
    export APPTAINER_NO_MOUNT="home,tmp,proc,sys,dev"
    export LC_ALL=C
    # Make the evaluator package importable regardless of the working directory
    export PYTHONPATH="/opt/martyn_evaluator:$PYTHONPATH"
    
%post
    # Install system packages and dependencies
    echo "Installing system dependencies..."
    apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends python3-pip bzip2 ca-certificates && \
    apt-get clean && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

    echo "Installing Python dependencies..."
    python -m pip install --upgrade pip
    python -m pip install --no-cache-dir numpy tqdm pandas msgpack scipy requests
    
    # Set permissions to access all directories
    echo "Setting permissions for the evaluator scripts..."
    chmod -R 755 /opt/martyn_evaluator

%runscript
    exec python3 /opt/martyn_evaluator/evaluator_RestAPI.py "$@"

%startscript
    exec python3 /opt/martyn_evaluator/evaluator_RestAPI.py "$@"

%labels
    Author "Ishika Luthra, Satyam Priyadarshi"
    game_schema_version "1.0"
    Description "This container is the Evaluator set up for Genomic API for Model Evaluation for Martyn et al. (2025) Variant Effects dataset."

%help
    Martyn Variant Effects evaluator (PPIF & IL2RA promoter/enhancer variant effects,
    THP-1 and Jurkat). Sends one /predict request per cell type to a Predictor and writes a
    single tab-separated summary: evaluation_summary_<evaluator_name>.csv.

    The image contains ONLY the evaluator scripts. The input data is provided at runtime by
    bind-mounting your evaluator_data directory to /evaluator_data, and predictions are written
    to a mounted predictions directory. config.py auto-detects the container and reads /evaluator_data.

    Build (from inside the evaluator directory):
        ```
        apptainer build martyn_evaluator.sif martyn_evaluator.def
        ```

    Run:
        ```
        apptainer run \
          -B /abs/path/to/evaluator_data:/evaluator_data \
          -B /abs/path/to/predictions:/predictions \
          martyn_evaluator.sif PREDICTOR_HOST PREDICTOR_PORT /predictions
        ```

    Arguments:
        1. `PREDICTOR_HOST` : IP address or hostname of the Predictor server.
        2. `PREDICTOR_PORT` : Port the Predictor is listening on.
        3. `/predictions` : Mounted path inside the container for predictions + summary CSV.

